.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-7::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: roller, bus, scooter, van
1. the person driving the bus is between the person driving the scooter and the person driving the roller##2
2. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
3. the person driving the roller is between the person driving the van and the person driving the bus##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |   3   |    4     |
| Transport   | scooter | bus | roller | van |

