.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-2-8::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, action, spy, time-travel
1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far left##1
2. the person watching spy movies is between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching time-travel movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4     |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | spy | time-travel | action |

