2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is between the person who's birthday is in september and the person who's birthday is in december##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |   2    |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday   | september | july | december | may |

